    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my go-to for weekend cruises and has never missed a beat. She\u2019s in wonderful shape and still turns heads at every stoplight with that classic look. I\u2019ve taken great care of her, and while she\u2019s got a little 'character' from a few years of happy driving, she runs smooth as silk and is ready for her next adventure. I'm really looking for someone who will appreciate the soul of this car as much as I have. Come on by, let's chat cars, and take her for a spin\u2014I promise you'll leave with a smile!",
