    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, a final-run specimen of the high-revving S65 V8 era. This chassis is remarkably tight, benefiting from a comprehensive preventative maintenance regimen including treated rod bearing shells and reinforced throttle actuators to ensure peak reciprocating assembly longevity. The DCT transmission has been flashed with GTS-spec software for lightning-quick engagement and optimized shift points. Underneath, the subframe bushings are resilient, and the suspension geometry remains true, delivering the precise lateral feedback and torsional rigidity these M-cars are known for. The induction roar from the naturally aspirated mill is visceral, with a linear power delivery that pulls hard all the way to the 8,400 RPM redline. This is an enthusiast-owned driver\u2019s car, dialed in for immediate canyon duty or high-speed touring.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
